                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 259). I took the prisoner—I produce another pair of boots, which I received from Mr. Capel, a pawn<lb></lb>broker.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360404-name-554" type="witnessName">
